node.text:
Bobby Walden of @waldenspeedshop finishes off the second corner panel and bead with his #pullmax and #yoder hammer 💪 Incredible metal shaping with hood instruction #baileighamy #baileighpowerhammer #baileighmetalshaping #beadrolling #metalshaping 
📷 @mad_fabricators

node.text:
Bobby Walden @waldenspeedshop is like the #bobross of the #yoder hammer. You almost get emotional watching his bedside manner as he passes down his craft to the next generation. Who thinks we should send Bobby a big Bob Ross wig for the next episode? #baileigharmy #waldenhammerworks #baileighpowerhammer #pullmax #metalshaping 
📷 @mad_fabricators

Top shelf metal shaping on the 32 Roadster Pickup by Bobby Walden at @waldenspeedshop 💪 He uses the MH-19 #baileighpowerhammer and PH-36A #baileighplanishinghammer in addition to his old school tricks on the #pullmax and MSS-14F #baileighshrinkerstretcher 
📷 @mad_fabricators #baileigharmy
